dismissalText.commentary: Marnus Labuschagne lbw b Jadeja 29 (36b 2x4 1x6 49m) SR: 80.55

dismissalComment.html: Trapped on the crease and in front of the stumps. The umpire's finger is up in a flash and Labuschagne will not review. Jadeja bowls this much quicker and his usual wicket to wicket line. Labuschagne is back and looks to work this away to the on-side. Misses and is trapped in front. Ball-tracker brings up an umpire's call on leg stump. So Labuschagne would have had to walk back even on review
